un nisht tsu geyn nokh azelkhe narishkeytn ongetuekhts,

00:11:06.259 --> 00:11:11.057
vayl der iker iz vos m'iz inevendik, nisht vos der oyser fun di kleyder zenen.

00:11:11.198 --> 00:11:13.709
un az di Gemore zogt az far vos in Bovl

00:11:13.709 --> 00:11:18.417
iz men gegangen ongetun sheyn, vayl di mentshn zenen nisht geven azelkhe groyse talmide-khakhomim,

00:11:18.417 --> 00:11:23.580
ver s'a rikhtiker talmed-khokhem darf nisht zayn ongeton sheyn, er vet shoyn mimeyle visn ver er iz.

00:11:23.580 --> 00:11:29.062
iz mimeyle bet er UNK hot er vegn dem geshribn dem briv, iz take di hut hob ikh nisht bakumen.

00:11:33.186 --> 00:11:39.592
dos iz der seyfer Minkhas Yosef. der Minkhas Yosef dos iz fun ksav-yad,

00:11:39.767 --> 00:11:44.756
vos m'hot gefunen fun tatn, vayl leyder di merste ksav-yad hot men tsugenumen.

00:11:45.032 --> 00:11:49.450
nor a bisl, iz farloyrn gegangen. nor a bisl ksav-yad iz geblibn,

00:11:49.450 --> 00:11:52.589
hot es mayn bruder tsuzamen geshtelt, tsuzamen geshlept,

00:11:52.589 --> 00:11:59.015
un er hot gema- gedrukt gemakht derfun dem seyfer Minkhas Yosef tsvey khalokim. der ershter kheylek iz oyf der toyre,

00:11:59.140 --> 00:12:02.981
un der tsveyter kheylek iz oyf shayles-utshuves.

00:12:03.882 --> 00:12:10.173
iz leyder s'nisht geblibn keyn sakh. dos hot gemakht der bruder, der bruder voynt haynt, er hot gevoynt in Kanade,

00:12:10.173 --> 00:12:13.395
un er hot es gemakht, gedrukt in Erets-Yisroel hot er es gedrukt,

00:12:13.395 --> 00:12:21.099
der seyfer, un l- leyder hot men shoyn nisht derfun un epes ksav-yad iz nokh do, ober s'iz nisht

00:12:21.099 --> 00:12:23.231
s'leyder nishto mer ksav-yad.

00:12:29.346 --> 00:12:32.608
koydesh kislev in,

00:12:32.535 --> 00:12:33.643
vos iz dos?

00:12:33.700 --> 00:12:40.021
dos iz di ksube. o dos iz di ksube vos iz gemakht gevorn in Mishkolts, efsher di ershte ksube nokh der milkhome.

00:12:40.021 --> 00:12:44.930
s'gevezn m'hot nisht gekent, s'nisht geven tsu koyfn makhn shener sheyne ksubes,

00:12:44.930 --> 00:12:46.748
m'hot nisht in zin gehat azelkhe zakhn,

00:12:46.748 --> 00:12:52.589
dos iz gevezn dem drit- montik, dos heyst, SORRY, dinstik iz es gevezn,

00:12:52.589 --> 00:13:03.759
in tov shin tov shin mem bey- tov shin beys iz es gevezn z- in tsvey un tsvontsik tog in khoydesh kislev,

00:13:03.759 --> 00:13:05.756
iz es gevezn tsu shnas,

00:13:06.825 --> 00:13:13.822
tsvey un tsvontsik tog in khoydesh kislev, yo ikh hob shoyn gezogt, iz geven gemakht geven undzer khasene, un dos iz di ksube vos iz demolts gevezn.

00:13:13.930 --> 00:13:18.834
vos iz gevorn, di khasene iz gevezn leyder nisht a khasene vos m'makht

00:13:18.874 --> 00:13:21.807
haynt, s'geven leyder a khasene vos iz geven koym koym

00:13:21.807 --> 00:13:24.859
tsamshlepn a minyen, s'nisht geven mer keyn yidn dortn.

00:13:31.412 --> 00:13:35.552
dos iz stam a kartl, vos m'hot gegebn yedn eynem,

00:13:35.552 --> 00:13:44.029
hot men gegebn, s'a dokument tsu vayzn in Daytshland az m'voynt in Poking. dos iz,

00:13:48.068 --> 00:13:53.397
dos iz geven dos iz geven der der lager iz gevezn flegt men tsu a- m'hot gearbet,

00:13:53.397 --> 00:13:56.679
ven m'hot gearbet hot men gegebn peklekh, vos m'hot nisht gegebn keyn gelt

00:13:56.679 --> 00:13:59.691
zey hobn gegebn peklekh. vos hot men gegebn? m'hot gegebn tsigaretlekh,

00:13:59.691 --> 00:14:02.625
hot men gegebn, s'geven ayngeteylt farshidene kategoryes.

00:14:02.665 --> 00:14:05.159
iz dos iz geven vos iz do, s'geven a a

00:14:05.159 --> 00:14:13.290
a kartl tsu vayzn az ikh hob gearbet dortn, un dos iz geven der datum iz der geven zekstn in in JULY, in zibn un fertsik.

00:14:13.296 --> 00:14:16.288
hob ikh dort bakumen dos, dort iz geven s'geven untergeshribn Halpern,

00:14:16.288 --> 00:14:21.408
dos iz geven d- zey hobn gevust az m'iz gekumen ahin bakumen di peklekh. di peklekh iz gevezn

00:14:21.450 --> 00:14:26.904
tsigaretlekh, kave, un dos als nor UNK, vayl m'hot gegebn tsu esn hot men gegebn tsu esn

00:14:26.904 --> 00:14:31.413
normal tsu esn iz geven dortn. un vos iz gevezn shoyn UNK, hakel reyvekh.

00:14:35.976 --> 00:14:41.218
deys iz an andere dokument vos tsu vayzn az ikh bin dokh az ikh hob gevoynt in Poking,

00:14:41.218 --> 00:14:46.445
vayl s'geven vikhtik tsu vayzn m'g- az m'fort hot men legitimirt m'zol visn ver ver ikh bin.

00:14:46.445 --> 00:14:52.879
iz dos geven a sertifikat az ikh voyn az ikh bin a aynvoyner fun lager Poking. Valdshtat.

00:14:59.432 --> 00:15:05.315
dos iz a geburt-shayn fun Mendl, az er iz geboyrn in Daytshland.

00:15:06.317 --> 00:15:09.857
ober dos iz shoyn ibergezetst, vayl s'gevezn oyfn oyf english.

00:15:09.857 --> 00:15:13.350
hot men gebroykht tsu hobn es ven m'iz gekumen aher,

00:15:13.350 --> 00:15:15.980
hot men dos gebroykht tsu hobn dos, hot men dos gemakht oyf english.

00:15:23.277 --> 00:15:26.556
dos iz a dokument mit dem vos ze'mir geforn,

00:15:26.556 --> 00:15:28.829
mir ho'mir nisht gehat keyn pasport, zenen nokh gevezn

00:15:28.829 --> 00:15:34.340
shtet-loz, m'hot nisht gehat keyn keyn rekht in ergets nisht, iz befor ze'mir geforn oyf,

00:15:34.414 --> 00:15:36.888
vayl ikh hob gehat papirn tsu forn oyf Tshile,

00:15:36.912 --> 00:15:43.150
un azoy vi ikh hob gehat papirn tsu forn oyf Tshile, hob men gemuzt koydem, s'nisht geven keyn konsulat iz nisht gevezn in Daytshland,

00:15:43.240 --> 00:15:47.430
hot men gemuzt forn oyf Pariz. in Pariz iz gevezn der a konsulat,

00:15:47.430 --> 00:15:52.582
hot men gemakht di papirn, ze'mir geforn ariber ahin oyf oyf Tshi- oyf Pariz.

00:15:52.757 --> 00:15:57.037
un dos iz der dokument. m'hot gebroykht, geven dort in Pariz ze'mir gevezn a lange tsayt.

00:15:57.128 --> 00:16:04.091
m'hot gebroykht yede dray khadoshim m'hot gebroykht tsu farlengern dem dem dokument, dem oyfnthalt.

00:16:04.317 --> 00:16:05.981
UNK.

00:16:11.083 --> 00:16:17.172
deys iz a dokument, befor m'fort aroys hot men gebroykht tsu hobn a dokument az m'iz keyn mol nisht gevorn

00:16:17.172 --> 00:16:22.217
geCHARGED, m'iz nisht gevorn farmishpet tsu keyn shum zakh nisht. zey hobn, di politsey hot mit mir nisht keyn

00:16:22.217 --> 00:16:26.417
keyn TIK hobn zey nisht fun mir. un ikh hof zey veln vayter nisht hobn.

00:16:32.194 --> 00:16:39.464
azoy vi ikh hob shoyn gehat di papirn tsu forn oyf oyf Pariz, dos heyst forn forn oyf Tshile hot es geheysn demolts,

00:16:39.464 --> 00:16:43.376
ikh for oyf Pari- oyf Oystralye, iz

00:16:43.703 --> 00:16:46.973
hot men mir gezogt fun Dzhoynt, hot men mir gezogt, zolst visn

00:16:46.973 --> 00:16:51.951
az tomer, un m'zukht in Oystralye zukht men hoyzn-shnayders,

00:16:51.951 --> 00:16:56.068
farshidene arbayters, ober nisht keyn RABBIS. keyn RABBIS zukhn zey nisht beshum oyfn nisht.

00:16:56.068 --> 00:16:58.250
un oyb ikh vel forn ikh vel geyn mit bord,

00:16:58.250 --> 00:17:02.204
vestu keyn vestu nisht kenen forn. m'vet dikh nisht lozn, der konsulat vet dikh nisht lozn forn.

00:17:02.204 --> 00:17:05.568
iz farn ikh gey tsum konsulat, zol ikh mikh opshern di bord.

00:17:05.568 --> 00:17:08.226
a klal, ikh hob gefregt farshidene eytses,

00:17:08.226 --> 00:17:11.112
ale hobn gezogt, yo, vos heyst, s'geven di milkhome in Koree,

00:17:11.112 --> 00:17:14.998
m'zol loyfn, loyfn zol ikh, shoyn zolst kenen forn, ikh zol kenen forn oyf Oystralye.

00:17:15.057 --> 00:17:18.088
a klal, bin ikh geforn, gegangen, ikh hob mir opgeshoyrn di bord,

00:17:18.262 --> 00:17:22.588
un un ikh hob opgeshoyrn di bord, bin ikh geven in besmedresh iz geven a groyser

00:17:22.588 --> 00:17:25.347
tuml, hayitokhn? UNK hob ikh zey gezogt, herts mikh oys,

00:17:25.347 --> 00:17:27.642
ikh hob nisht gevolt dertseyln di gantse mayse far vos,

00:17:27.642 --> 00:17:31.840
hob ikh zey gezogt az s'geve- ikh hob gez- farloyrn gelt in shtub,

00:17:31.864 --> 00:17:35.641
un s'hot zikh gemakht, ikh hob genumen a likht, ikh hob es gezukht, ikh hob gemakht a sreyfe,

00:17:35.641 --> 00:17:39.823
un s'hot zikh gemakht a sreyfe hob ikh shoyn m'hot gemuzt aropnemen di gantse bord.

00:17:39.964 --> 00:17:42.675
ober interesant iz geven, ven ikh bin gekumen tsum konsul,

00:17:43.373 --> 00:17:45.977
hob i- hob ikh gemeynt, ikh kum shoyn tsum konsulat

00:17:46.004 --> 00:17:48.550
vet er shoyn zikher nisht hobn keyn shum trakhtenisher.

00:17:48.550 --> 00:17:54.521
di ershte shayle vos der konsul hot gefregt, "AREN'T YOU A RABBI?" hot er mikh gefregt.

00:17:54.645 --> 00:17:56.591
zog ikh farn konsulat,

00:17:56.591 --> 00:18:00.067
WHY DO YOU THINK, far vos trakhtstu az ikh bin a a RABBI?

00:18:00.067 --> 00:18:05.980
zogt er, der WAY vos ikh kum, vayl dort er iz gezesn inevendik, un s'gevezn a groyse koridor.

00:18:05.980 --> 00:18:09.571
zogt er, di WAY azoy vi ikh gey, gey ikh punkt vi a RABBI.

00:18:09.715 --> 00:18:13.010
shoyn, hob ikh ikh makh, hob ikh gezogt, ikh vel zogn dem emes.

00:18:13.010 --> 00:18:18.343
az mayn tate iz gevezn a RABBI, er hot undz gelozt lernen tsu zayn a RABBI,

00:18:18.343 --> 00:18:23.034
nor azoy vi s'gevorn di milkhome, hob ikh gezen az fun keyn RABBI vel ikh keyn lebn nisht makhn.

00:18:23.034 --> 00:18:25.268
bin ikh gegangen ikh hob mikh oysgelernt fakhn,

00:18:25.268 --> 00:18:28.950
vegn dem ikh hob ikh mir oysgelernt hitstert tsu makhn leder WORKER,

00:18:28.950 --> 00:18:33.200
un er zest dokh az ikh hob dortn iz oyfgeshribn az ikh bin a kapl makher,

00:18:33.200 --> 00:18:35.791
un az UNK az ikh ken di ale fakhn ken ikh,

00:18:35.791 --> 00:18:40.518
az ikh kum oyf Oystralye, zol ikh kenen makhn fun dos a a lebn un nisht fun RABBI.

00:18:40.518 --> 00:18:43.225
nu, s'im gefeln gevorn, hot er dos ongenumen.

00:18:43.225 --> 00:18:47.542
un mimeyle vegn dem ikh hob ikh nokh a bild on a bord azoy vi ikh hob oysgezen.

00:18:50.721 --> 00:18:52.827
un azoy ikh hob shoyn gemuzt hobn a fakh,

00:18:52.827 --> 00:18:56.671
andersh ken men nisht forn. un ikh hob nisht keyn shum ts- keyn tsetl nisht derfun,

00:18:56.745 --> 00:19:02.311
bin ikh gegangen in Ort, in Ort hob ikh genumen, ikh hob mikh oysgelernt, ikh hob gemakht der dem briv-tash,

00:19:02.311 --> 00:19:07.930
nor vos den, azoy vi s'gevezn eyn vos iz a shvere, vayl s'shoyn nisht geven keyn tsayt, vayl s'shoyn gevezn mamesh farn endikn,

00:19:07.930 --> 00:19:11.634
un makhn mit zeyere mashinen er hot nisht gevust, hob ikh gevust ikh vel nisht kenen.

00:19:11.634 --> 00:19:13.929
bin ikh gegangen, ikh hob genumen mayn moyel meserl,

00:19:13.929 --> 00:19:17.380
un ikh hob genumen, mit dem hob ikh es opgesharft dem leder baym ek,

00:19:17.380 --> 00:19:21.523
un ikh hob es ts- gemakht, tsu ales tsugeshnitn, ales geven zeyer sheyn aroysgekumen

00:19:21.523 --> 00:19:23.742
un tsum sof hob ikh bakumen a tsertifikat.

00:19:23.742 --> 00:19:27.024
nor vos den, ikh hob nisht bakumen keyn hundert protsentike tsertifikat,

00:19:27.024 --> 00:19:32.804
far vos, vayl ikh hob geton a groyse feler. vos iz geven der feler? ikh hob es geneyt farkert oyf der mashin.

00:19:32.804 --> 00:19:35.765
ikh hob es take aleyn geneyt, un ikh hob gevust es shoyn tsu neyen,

00:19:35.765 --> 00:19:40.364
ober az m'zol es neyen farkert, hob ikh nisht az s'a khilek az m'leygt arayn farkert azoy tsu azoy,

00:19:40.364 --> 00:19:43.636
mimeyle ober al kol ponem, a k- a tsertifikat hob ikh bakumen,

00:19:43.636 --> 00:19:48.318
un mit dem bin ikh gekumen oyf Oystralye als a leder WORKER, mit dem briv-tash.

00:19:48.484 --> 00:19:51.481
un dos hob ikh nokh azoy, leyg ikh es avek lezeykher.

00:19:55.032 --> 00:19:59.615
dos iz der zeyde mayner, dem tatn's tate, reb Nokhem.

00:19:59.655 --> 00:20:01.994
er hot gevoynt in Kemetsh hot er gevoynt,

00:20:02.052 --> 00:20:06.073
un er iz geven a yid a groyser erlekher yid, er iz geven zeyer a kluger yid.

00:20:06.073 --> 00:20:09.892
ikh hob getrofn a a eyner vos er voynt in Kemetsh,

00:20:09.932 --> 00:20:13.954
hot er mir a mol gezogt az, oysgekumen a shmues,

00:20:13.954 --> 00:20:16.299
zogt zi, ir zent reb Nokhem's an eynikl?

00:20:16.299 --> 00:20:19.277
zogt er, aza klugn yid vi reb Nokhem iz gevezn

00:20:19.277 --> 00:20:22.632
hot zi nokh nisht getrofn. er hot gehat a shem fun a klugn yid.

00:20:22.875 --> 00:20:28.348
un nebekh ikh ho- ikh hob im nokh ikh hob im nokh gekent, nor ikh hob gevust iber im veynik. er ligt in Pest.

00:20:28.348 --> 00:20:30.972
ven ikh bin gevezn in Pest, bin ikh gevezn oyfn beys-akvores,

00:20:30.972 --> 00:20:33.858
freg ikh dortn dem shoymer fun fun dem,

00:20:33.858 --> 00:20:37.908
efsher veyst ir vu ligt do mayn zeyde reb Nokhem Heymlekh? o!

00:20:37.910 --> 00:20:43.390
dortn pinktlekh hot er es gevust oyfn plats, der ershter blik hot er bald gevust vu UNK, vu er ligt.

00:20:48.222 --> 00:20:57.261
dos iz der zeyde fun Korat. di di mame's eltern. tate un der mame's, tate un mame's mame.

00:20:57.351 --> 00:20:59.977
zey zenen geshtorbn eygntlekh in eyn tog.

00:21:00.102 --> 00:21:03.296
dos heyst zey zenen gevorn fargazt. vayl er iz geven a groyser oysher,

00:21:03.296 --> 00:21:08.803
kuk nisht oyfn hut, vosere hut er hot, nor er iz geven a yid a groyser oysher iz er gevezn,

00:21:08.944 --> 00:21:12.594
un er iz geforn oyf zumer, vinter iz er geforn

00:21:12.594 --> 00:21:15.681
oyf Karlsbad, Maryenbad, dort yener gegnt,

00:21:15.717 --> 00:21:19.490
un er hot gevoynt in a dort in Korat, iz er nisht geven gevoynt tsu keyn gaz.

00:21:19.490 --> 00:21:22.672
dort iz shoyn gevezn gaz-oyvns iz shoyn geven dortn,

00:21:22.672 --> 00:21:28.074
un zet m'hot nisht farmakht dem gaz vi es darf tsu zayn, zenen zey nebekh beyde gevorn fargazt dortn.

00:21:27.827 --> 00:21:29.289
vos iz zayn nomen?

00:21:28.992 --> 00:21:33.828
zayn nomen iz Mortkhe Itsik Samet, un di babe iz gevezn Pesl Samet.

00:21:34.020 --> 00:21:38.008
un er hot gehat eydemer, er iz geven a groyser oysher, hot er gehat eydemer

00:21:38.008 --> 00:21:43.036
loyter talmide-khakhomim, hot er nokh gelozt a sakh gelt, un er hot gehat a gvaldik groyse

00:21:43.036 --> 00:21:45.269
a groyse vertshaft hot er gehat bay zikh.

00:21:45.580 --> 00:21:51.412
un er iz geven a groyser Kerestirer khosid. Kerestirer hot er gegebn a sakh gelt oyf Kerestir.

00:21:52.988 --> 00:21:57.018
un zayn matseyve, o zayn matseyve shteyt nokh haynt

00:21:57.018 --> 00:22:02.595
in Korat. iz gevezn a, er hot gehat a goy vos der goy hot geheysn Ontol Batshi.

00:22:02.595 --> 00:22:07.995
er hot gearbet bay im yorn yorn lang. nokh der milkhome, in der milkhome heyst es,

00:22:07.995 --> 00:22:10.717
iz er hot, un nokh hitstert nokh der milkhome, nokh bay di rusn,

00:22:10.740 --> 00:22:14.188
hot er hot men gevolt tsunemen dem gantsn beys-akvores,

00:22:14.188 --> 00:22:19.526
hot er gezogt az der Samet di mishpokhe Samet lot er nisht beshum oyfn nisht.

00:22:19.600 --> 00:22:28.355
oyb m'vil es t- BULLDOZEn iz nor durkh zayn kerper. iz geblibn der zeyde, di babe, un a mume, iz geblibn der gantser keyver.

00:22:28.355 --> 00:22:32.362
interesant iz az eyn mayner a geshvesterkind vos hot gevoynt in Korat

00:22:32.362 --> 00:22:34.893
iz geforn oyf Korat, dort hot der goy gelebt,

00:22:34.893 --> 00:22:38.125
un er hot im dertseylt di gantse mayse un er hot es gelozt farrekhtn

00:22:38.125 --> 00:22:42.006
mit CONCRETE s'zol zayn zeyer gut. dem andern tog iz der goy geshtorbn.

00:22:42.006 --> 00:22:44.433
er iz shoyn alt geven kimat hundert yor, geven der goy.

00:22:47.747 --> 00:22:51.808
azoy hob ikh oysgezen in Poking. hob ikh azoy oysgezen.

00:22:52.017 --> 00:22:53.394
vi alt host geven?

00:22:53.265 --> 00:22:55.284
bin ikh alt geven dray un tsvontsik yor.

00:22:55.611 --> 00:22:58.760
mayn yidene hot gehaltn az ikh ze oys vi eyner vos iz alt finef un fertsik.

00:23:03.357 --> 00:23:09.876
dos iz a sh- a vi nokh geheysn, a TEUDA

00:23:09.769 --> 00:23:10.809
a COPY.

00:23:09.876 --> 00:23:17.154
a COPY fun dem vos ven der tate, fun der vos m'get ven der tate iz, fun vos der tate iz geshtorbn in Daytshland.

00:23:17.211 --> 00:23:21.204
dos hot keyner nisht bakumen, dos iz kimat nishto aza zakh.

00:23:21.227 --> 00:23:25.628
ven ikh bin geven in Daytshland hob ikh gefregt vi kumt dos az s'zol zayn?

00:23:25.628 --> 00:23:32.142
hobn zey nokhgekukt in bikhl, iz geven dort ayngeshribn, ober keyn anderer mentsh iz keyner nisht ayngeshribn nor er.

00:23:32.142 --> 00:23:34.547
vos dos iz farshtey ikh nisht un ikh veys nisht.

00:23:34.547 --> 00:23:42.113
ober al kol ponem, s'gevezn a zakh min-ashomaim, vos durkh dem bin ikh gevoyer gevorn pinktlekh vu der tate ligt.

00:23:42.118 --> 00:23:45.574
bin ikh gevoyer gevorn er iz geven az er ligt in Daytshland, bin ikh geven dortn,

00:23:45.574 --> 00:23:54.603
hob ikh bakumen az er ligt dortn nisht vayt fun fun Kovbayern, iz a shtikl veg fun dortn. in in a feld.

00:23:54.603 --> 00:23:58.636
vos dort iz geven der lager iz geven dort. UNK zet men shoyn gornisht, ikh bin geven dortn,

00:23:58.687 --> 00:24:02.392
m'zet dortn gornisht keyn shum lager nisht, alts bavaksn dortn,

00:24:02.392 --> 00:24:08.574
nor vos m'zet iz do a az do a s'do leydiker plats, s'hot a geder,

00:24:08.574 --> 00:24:15.028
un der geder, dort iz do dray matseyves, hob ikh shoyn nisht gevolt shteln dort keyn matseyve, ikh hob nor geshtelt a

00:24:15.028 --> 00:24:17.921
a shteyn, oyf der vant hob ikh es geshtelt.

00:24:18.703 --> 00:24:22.067
vifl mol m'iz gekumen zukhn dem vu dem vu dos iz,

00:24:22.092 --> 00:24:26.501
iz alts geshen interesante zakh. m'iz gekumen, vu iz ⟨doses⟩ plats hot keyner nisht gevust.

00:24:26.501 --> 00:24:31.774
iz eyn mol gekumen stam a goy iz gekumen, zogt er mir azoy, o, ikh veys vu s'iz. punkt damolts

00:24:31.774 --> 00:24:33.797
iz er arayngekumen dort in di IRIYA,

00:24:33.797 --> 00:24:39.297
in der shtot-hoyz iz er arayngekumen, er hot mir gezogt vu dos iz. un di tsveyte mol vi gekumen iz gekumen a goye

00:24:39.297 --> 00:24:43.206
un zi hot punkt gehat a ACCIDENT, a vokh frier hot zi gehat an ACCIDENT derlebn,

00:24:43.206 --> 00:24:47.616
undz ze'mir gekumen, hot zi gevust pinktlekh vu es iz, azoy iz zi gekumen mir vayzn vu s'iz.

00:24:47.616 --> 00:24:53.581
un dos dort hot zi mir, dos iz dos plats. un bin ikh gevoyer gevorn nokh dem, der plats iz gekumen iz fun Riderlikh,

00:24:53.581 --> 00:24:57.476
ober der Riderlikh ekzistirt shoyn haynt nisht. zey visn nisht vu dos iz.

00:24:57.752 --> 00:25:02.145
un al kol ponem iz di yidn in Daytshland, in Minkhn,

00:25:02.145 --> 00:25:04.931
hob ikh zey, zey geyen a mol on tsum tsien,

00:25:04.945 --> 00:25:07.672
vayl ikh hob zey gezogt, koydem kol gehaltn dortn, lign dortn

00:25:07.672 --> 00:25:11.445
nokh a fir hundert andere yidn lign oykh dortn.

00:25:11.445 --> 00:25:15.721
un hob ikh zey gezogt az der eyner hot er broykh tsu hobn a yeshue

00:25:15.721 --> 00:25:19.813
zol er geyn ahin, vet er geholfn vern. un zey hobn take gezen az s'iz take azoy.

00:25:19.813 --> 00:25:22.791
un ay vi vi hob ikh mikh getroyt aza zakh tsu zogn?

00:25:22.791 --> 00:25:27.295
az s'lign dortn fir hundert kdoyshim, muz es muz es helfn.

00:25:28.498 --> 00:25:31.512
un s'zol take helfn vayter. zkhusom yogn oleynu.

00:25:34.320 --> 00:25:37.844
iz di der dokument iz, nokh dem ven ikh hob bakumen dem

00:25:37.844 --> 00:25:41.081
DEATH CERTIFICATE fun di yekes fun di daytshn,

00:25:41.121 --> 00:25:43.269
hob ikh geshribn far der Royte Kreyts

00:25:43.269 --> 00:25:50.112
un ikh hob gevolt pinktlekh mer DETAILS tsu visn oyb oyb zey hobn shoyn UNK, vos vos vo- vos nokh visn zey fun tatn, vos iz gevezn.

00:25:50.112 --> 00:25:54.128
iz dos di dokumentn vos shikn arayn. vos zey hobn mir arayngeshikt.

00:25:54.128 --> 00:25:58.364
un kedey durkh tsu kukn. leyder visn zey nisht mer azoy fil, er iz geven a yid,

00:25:58.364 --> 00:26:06.591
far vos er iz geshtorbn veysn zey nisht, ver er iz geshtorbn veysn zey nisht, vu er iz geshtorbn veysn zey nisht. dos iz gornisht, s'gornisht s'iz s'gornisht UNK,

00:26:06.591 --> 00:26:12.387
un vayzt dikh vos di daytshn dos hobn zey, khuts dem vos zey hobn mir gezogt di dem nomen, dertsu veysn zey gornisht.

00:26:12.087 --> 00:26:14.649
nor zey zogn do az er hot gekumen fun AUSCHWITZ.

00:26:12.387 --> 00:26:14.155
m'hot im m'hot im geCATERED.

00:26:15.445 --> 00:26:17.551
ober gekumen iz er fun Oyshvits, yo az er iz geven

00:26:17.551 --> 00:26:24.773
geven in Oysh- dos veyst men, m'hot gerufn tsu UNK. fun Mishkolts hot men gefirt oyf Oyshvits, un fun Oyshvits hot men gefirt dort ahin tsu arbetn dortn,

00:26:24.773 --> 00:26:27.470
ober dos iz es, mer veyst men nisht gornisht.

00:26:30.953 --> 00:26:36.532
zey antshuldikn zikh do oyf UNK. zey shraybn a VEY SORRY UNK.

00:26:43.002 --> 00:26:49.290
dos iz di shteyn, dos heyst der tovl, vos ikh hob geshtelt oyf der vant hob ikh es geshtelt,

00:26:49.296 --> 00:26:54.912
fun tatn, hob ikh es do oyfgeshribn der tate poshet als ver er iz, un ver der foter hot geheysn,

00:26:54.912 --> 00:27:01.609
un keyn matseyve hob ikh nisht gekent shteln, vayl ikh hob nisht gevust, vayl m'hot vu ikh hob moyre gehat vu ikh shtel es vet es zayn kvorim vet zayn dortn.

00:27:02.172 --> 00:27:05.878
iz mimeyle dos iz di shteyn vos ikh hob geshtalt fun danet, ikh hob geshikt fun danet.

00:27:10.980 --> 00:27:17.153
dos iz a bild fun a fun mir, un mayn vayb un un nokh di tsvey kinderlekh,

00:27:17.153 --> 00:27:21.268
un der shvoger, der Ratsferter rebe un mayn shvester Pesl.

00:27:21.561 --> 00:27:24.637
un zi hot nisht gehat keyn kinder nokh, halt zi undzere tsvey kinder.

00:27:24.637 --> 00:27:32.051
eyner elterer vos mame halt, Golde halt, iz der iz Mendl, un der kleyner, dos pitsele, iz Shiele.

00:27:35.314 --> 00:27:40.938
dos iz a bild fun mayn bruder Yoyl vos er iz geven di gantse tsayt in der milkhome,

00:27:40.938 --> 00:27:45.163
un haynt iz er oykh borekh-hashem gezunt un borekh-hashem er voynt haynt in Amerike.

00:27:49.629 --> 00:27:54.140
dos iz Mendl, mit zayne khevre, mit zayne kinderlekh keyn eyn-hore,

00:27:55.800 --> 00:28:00.215
un vi azoy heyst es shoyn, hot er kimat ale shoyn khasene gehat hitstert.

00:28:09.013 --> 00:28:13.918
dos iz der zun, mayn tsveyter zun, Shiele, vos er voynt in Bney-Brak,

00:28:13.958 --> 00:28:16.230
un er hot khasene gehat keyn eyn-hore di tokhter,

00:28:16.236 --> 00:28:23.047
hot er khasene gemakht, un dos iz al- kimat ale zayne tekhter. dos heyst di gantse mishpokhe zayne hot er iz azoy.

00:28:27.019 --> 00:28:31.940
dos iz der driter zun mayner, Noyekh Yankev, er voynt in Yerusholaim.

00:28:32.149 --> 00:28:34.252
un keyn eyn-hore dos zenen zayne kleyne khevre.

00:28:34.258 --> 00:28:38.938
un di kleyne khevre hobn shoyn kimat ale khasene gehat, vos zenen do oyfn bild.

00:28:38.938 --> 00:28:43.567
nor hitst kumt der tsveyter bild kumt vos iz di gantse di iberike fun der mishpokhe.

00:28:46.594 --> 00:28:52.561
dos iz der bild vos iz der fun mayn dritn zun, dos iz di froy zayne mit ir muter,

00:28:52.770 --> 00:28:59.682
un s'a por shnurn fun tsveytn zun, un mit di ey- iberike zay- zayne eygene kinder keyn eyn-hore.

00:29:05.342 --> 00:29:09.099
dos iz a bild fun altn porfolk.

00:29:10.742 --> 00:29:14.282
ze'mir undz dos iz a bild fun der fun mayn vayb, fun Golde,

00:29:14.282 --> 00:29:17.655
un ikh. s'nisht keyn, dos deys gemakht nisht lang gemakht,

00:29:17.830 --> 00:29:21.013
az dakht zikh oykh gemakht dakht zikh mir in Erets-Yisroel shoyn gemakht.
